<label for="User Group">User Group</label>
 <angular2-multiselect [data]="userGroupdatalist" 
    [settings]="dropdownSettingsUG" 
    (onSelect)="onItemSelect($event)" 
    (onDeSelect)="OnItemDeSelect($event)"
    (onSelectAll)="onSelectAll($event)"
    (onDeSelectAll)="onDeSelectAll($event)"
    formControlName="userGroup"
    ></angular2-multiselect>

    <mat-error *ngIf="isSubmitted && getuserGroup.errors">* Select userGroup!!!</mat-error>

<!-- <mat-error [fxShow]='isSubmitted && form.invalid'>* Select userGroup!!!</mat-error> -->

<label for="Report Group">Report Group</label>
  <angular2-multiselect id="reportGroupdatalist" name="reportGroupdatalist" [data]="reportGroupdatalist"  
                                  [settings]="dropdownSettingsRG" 
                                  (onSelect)="onItemSelect($event)"
                                  (onDeSelect)="OnItemDeSelect($event)" 
                                  (onSelectAll)="onSelectAll($event)" 
                                  (onDeSelectAll)="onDeSelectAll($event)" formControlName="reportGroup">
            </angular2-multiselect>

<mat-error [fxShow]='isSubmitted && getReportGroup?.errors'>* Select reportGroup!!!</mat-error>
